OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FThe jury at the inquest into the death
OL,7,Fof Noah Donohoe have been told to
OL,8,Freach their findings based on the
OL,9,Fevidence they have heard in court.
OL,11,FCoroner Mr Justice Rooney started his
OL,12,Fcharge to the jury of eight men and
OL,13,Ftwo women on Thursday, on the 21st
OL,14,Fweek of the inquest, which started in
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
