OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,8,Fin the storm drain tunnel in north
OL,9,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,10,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,11,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FCCTV evidence and witnesses show that
OL,15,FNoah took a detour from his planned
OL,16,Froute, cycling instead along York Road
OL,17,Fand ended up on Northwood Road where
OL,18,Fit is suggested he entered the tunnel
OL,19,Fvia a culvert behind a house.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FThe inquest was shown CCTV of Noah
OL,7,Fcycling naked along Northwood Road,
OL,8,Fand evidence that some residents heard
OL,9,Fnoises including screams on the night
OL,10,Fof June 21 when Noah went missing.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,13,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,15,FThe jury is charged with reaching
OL,16,Ffindings including how Noah came by
OL,17,Fhis death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
