PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe, who has
OL,7,Fled a high profile campaign for
OL,8,Fanswers around his death, has been
OL,9,Fpresent at Belfast Coroner's Court for
OL,10,Fevery day of the inquest.
OL,12,FMr Justice Rooney told the jury his
OL,13,Fcharge would be lengthy as it covered
OL,14,Falmost six months of evidence.
OL,16,FHe said the inquest had heard from 76
OL,17,Fwitnesses, and statements from a
OL,18,Ffurther 42 people, and considered
OL,19,Fmaps, video footage, photographs,
OL,20,Fpolice logs and expert reports.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
