FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FHe also reminded the jury the process
OL,7,Fwas a fact-finding inquiry into how
OL,8,FNoah died, and not a criminal trial
OL,9,Fwhere someone is found guilty of an
OL,10,Foffence or found liable to pay
OL,11,Fdamages, and not about finding fault,
OL,12,Fattributing blame or apportioning
OL,13,Fguilt.
OL,15,F"Your findings must be based solely on
OL,16,Fthe evidence that you have heard or
OL,17,Fhave seen in this court, you must
OL,18,Fignore everything else other than this
OL,19,Fevidence. It is irrelevant," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
