OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,F"We are here because this inquest is
OL,7,Frequired by law. You must not suppose
OL,8,Fthat this automatically means that
OL,9,Fsomething went wrong that contributed
OL,10,Fto Noah's death, you must not lose
OL,11,Ffocus on the question we are here to
OL,12,Fconsider, that is how Noah came by his
OL,13,Fdeath."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
