PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FSummarising the evidence heard, Mr
OL,7,FJustice Rooney recounted that Noah was
OL,8,Fa positive person who was popular and
OL,9,Fwell-liked, had a close bond with his
OL,10,Fmother, was a top academic achiever
OL,11,Faiming to study medicine at Trinity
OL,12,FCollege, Dublin and who was loved by
OL,13,Fhis family and friends.
OL,15,FHe said they were "not bound" by the
OL,16,Fcause of death given by pathologists
OL,17,Fas drowning, and may change it, but
OL,18,Fpointed out it was agreed by all the
OL,19,Fpathologists and had not been
OL,20,Fchallenged in the inquest.
OL,26,@wD@SOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
