FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FHe also cautioned the jury that they
OL,7,Fcould not make a number of findings
OL,8,Fthat there was no evidence to support.
OL,10,FThese included that there was
OL,11,Finsufficient evidence to find that
OL,12,FNoah was assaulted by a third party,
OL,13,Fthat Noah was under the influence of
OL,14,Fdrugs, that Noah was in a psychotic
OL,15,Fepisode or acute mental illness, that
OL,16,Fhe had taken his own life, that a
OL,17,Fthird party was responsible for his
OL,18,Fdeath or that he was the victim of
OL,19,Fchild exploitation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
