FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1782503276
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury told to
OL,4,Creach findings 'solely on evidence'
OL,6,FHe added that it is "not a failure" of
OL,7,Fthe inquest process that they had
OL,8,Freached a point where certain findings
OL,9,Fcould not be made.
OL,11,F"In fact the opposite is true, this is
OL,12,Fthe inquest process working properly,
OL,13,Fwe have tested extensively the
OL,14,Fevidence on these topics, it is only
OL,15,Fonce we have tested that evidence that
OL,16,Fwe can rule out it is more likely than
OL,17,Fnot that these matters did not
OL,18,Fhappen," he said.
OL,20,FThe coroner's summing-up of the
OL,21,Fevidence will resume on Monday morning.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@cO]sD@AOUzD@HO]
